# Nomos Repository Architecture

## Overview

This document describes the proposed repository architecture for the
**Nomos Protocol**, a reputation infrastructure for autonomous agents
operating in the Web4 AI economy.

The repository is designed with a modular structure to support:

-   agent identity management
-   behavioral signal ingestion
-   reputation computation
-   API services
-   SDK integrations
-   developer tooling
-   protocol research

The architecture follows common patterns used in modern AI and
infrastructure repositories.

